n quickly that HPs are very valuable to you as a necro...but you don;t get it without having actually played the class.  same for any class...if ya don't play it, save yerself from looking like an intellectual cluster-f*@# and keep your witty retorts to yourself.  simple fact, anyone can use it....but monks do get the most benefit from it.  take it for what it's worth and leave the rest alone.</p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
