es up. Maybe that's just my ranger mentality, perhaps if I was a drood or cleric I'd be more magnanimous =) <br><br>Anyway that's my 2 cp, etc - is this just me?<br><br>EDIT: I have now met some superb monks inside my guild, one of them being the GL, who have showed me what playing that class is all about, and are great players all round. I've also met a cleric who refused to rez a group member after a wipe because he didn't like him...which just go to show there are always exceptions ;-)<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Wed Oct&nbsp;&nbsp;1 10:38:22 2003</em></p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
