4 weight screams monk.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sat Mar 15 14:03:46 2003</em></p>&nbsp;<br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=286983 target=akztarg>Sage Branaddar Balefire</a><br>Wizard of the 65th Spire<br><br>Baron Razormaw Balefire<br>Monk of the 63rd Flurry<br><br>Tholuxe Paells</td></td></tr>
